== 評價 ==
本劇獲得電視影評家廣泛的好評。第1季於[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]整合的評論中獲得90%的新鮮度、平均得分8.42/10（71名評論家），評論家共識：「大膽、聰明以及視覺上的捕捉，使《變種軍團》以師級超現實與輝煌的氣魄和傳統超級英雄作品區隔開來。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/legion/s01/|title=Legion: Season 1|publisher=[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]|accessdate=2017-02-10|archive-date=2017-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170206224442/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/legion/s01/|dead-url=no}}</ref>於[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]整合的評論中，獲得了82分（滿分100；40名評論家），屬極佳的讚譽。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/legion|title=Legion - Season 1 Reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2017-02-10|archive-date=2017-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170210004935/http://www.metacritic.com/tv/legion|dead-url=no}}</ref>〈[[今日美國|今日美國]]〉、<ref name="USAReview">{{cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/tv/2017/02/07/fx-legion-marvel-noah-hawley-dan-stevens-robert-bianco/97407518/|title=Review: FX's 'Legion' is a complex, rewarding blend of humor and jolts|last=Bianco|first=Robert|work=[[今日美國|今日美國]]|date=2017-02-07|accessdate=2017-02-13|archive-date=2017-02-13|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6oEv39zG8?url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/tv/2017/02/07/fx-legion-marvel-noah-hawley-dan-stevens-robert-bianco/97407518/|dead-url=no}}</ref>〈[[舊金山紀事報|舊金山紀事報]]〉、<ref name="SFCReview">{{cite web|url=http://www.sfgate.com/tv/article/Legion-a-marvel-that-doesn-t-feel-like-a-10909108.php|title=‘Legion’ a marvel that doesn’t feel like a comic book|last=Wiegand|first=David|work=[[舊金山紀事報|舊金山紀事報]]|date=2017-02-05|accessdate=2017-02-13|archive-date=2017-02-13|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6oF1DTgvG?url=http://www.sfgate.com/tv/article/Legion-a-marvel-that-doesn-t-feel-like-a-10909108.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>〈[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝雜誌]]〉、<ref name="VarietyReview">{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2017/tv/reviews/legion-fx-dan-stevens-review-noah-hawley-1201974474/|title=TV Review: ‘Legion’ on FX, Starring Dan Stevens|last=Ryan|first=Maureen|work=綜藝雜誌|date=2017-02-01|accessdate=2017-02-13|archive-date=2017-02-09|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6o96aasWy?url=http://variety.com/2017/tv/reviews/legion-fx-dan-stevens-review-noah-hawley-1201974474/|dead-url=no}}</ref>〈[[荷里活報道|好萊塢報導]]〉<ref name="THRReview">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/legion-review-968837|title='Legion': TV Review|last=Goodman|first=Tim|work=好萊塢報導|date=2017-01-26|accessdate=2017-02-13|archive-date=2017-02-13|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6oF1WhIZs?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/legion-review-968837|dead-url=no}}</ref>與〈[[大西洋_(雜誌)|大西洋雜誌]]〉<ref name="AtlanticReview">{{cite web|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2017/02/legion-is-visually-dazzling-but-little-else/515850/|title=Legion Is Visually Dazzling, but Little Else|last=Sims|first=David|work=[[大西洋_(雜誌)|大西洋雜誌]]|date=2017-02-07|accessdate=2017-02-13|archive-date=2017-02-13|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6oEuzS6p2?url=https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2017/02/legion-is-visually-dazzling-but-little-else/515850/|dead-url=no}}</ref>等影評人皆給予[[丹·史蒂文斯|丹·史蒂文斯]]的演出許多好評，{{le|瑞秋·凱勒|Rachel Keller}}與[[珍·史瑪特|珍·史瑪特]]也收穫了一些表演上的稱讚。<ref name="USAReview"/>[[奧布瑞·克莉絲丁·普拉扎|奧布蕊·普拉薩]]在第6集的表演，更獲〈{{le|TVLine|TVLine}}〉評為當周最佳演出。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvline.com/2017/03/18/aubrey-plaza-legion-performance-season-1-lenny/ |title=TVLine's Performer of the Week: Legion's Aubrey Plaza |publisher=TVLine |date=2017-03-18 |accessdate=2017-03-20 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6p6FYfp3u?url=http://tvline.com/2017/03/18/aubrey-plaza-legion-performance-season-1-lenny/ |archivedate=2017-03-20 |deadurl=no }}</ref>

